class  RMLFlags
 Data structure containing flags to parameterize the execution of the Online Trajectory Generation algorithm. More...

Detailed Description

Header file for the class RMLFlags.

Flags to parameterize the Online Trajectory Generation algorithms. This basis data structure is inherited to the structures RMLPositionFlags and RMLVelocityFlags
